Facile grammar, by Alex Thornton

The start variable is [program].

{
[program]
[statement] NL . NL ;
[statement] NL [program] ;
[statement] NL [program] ;
[statement] NL [program] ;
[statement] NL [program] ;
[statement] NL [program] ;
